Have a savoury #Vegetarian meal here. There is a large variety of dishes to choose from and mixed with the fried noodles was just #YummyForMyTummy.

Sure to return for another visit.

Just found out about this vegetarian stall. It is inside the Koufu food court. The serving is quite generous and price is reasonable at $4.50 only. Quite delicious too. Will visit again when passing by.

Thank you to the honest staff who corrected it and refunded me, after her colleague accidentally overcharged me.

Her colleague charged me twice for 1 dish thinking that I had ordered a double portion. I couldnt really understand her and had just paid the price quoted.

She saw the miscommunication and immediately stepped in to correct it and refund me the amount.

We need more of such people around!
Freshly cooked vegetables and assorted vegetarian dishes. The tofu and curry veggies are worth a try.
